{"type":"message","id":"a2489a02","parentId":"af6e103f","timestamp":"2026-03-22T14:02:44.549Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，现在让我创建一个 README.md 文件来说明项目结构和使用方法。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_cd2d14ff4c6f480aab9cfa8c","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"# Tianyou.FormService - 云天佑表单服务\n\n云天佑低代码平台的核心 Web API 服务，提供表单管理、数据存储、插件加载等功能。\n\n## 技术栈\n\n- .NET 8\n- ASP.NET Core Web API\n- Entity Framework Core\n- PostgreSQL\n- Redis\n- Serilog (日志)\n\n## 项目结构\n\n```\nTianyou.FormService/\n├── Controllers/\n│   ├── FormController.cs      # 表单 API\n│   └── PluginController.cs    # 插件 API\n├── Program.cs                 # 应用入口\n├── appsettings.json           # 生产配置\n└── appsettings.Development.json # 开发配置\n```\n\n## 快速启动\n\n### 1. 安装依赖\n\n```bash\ncd services/Tianyou.FormService\ndotnet restore\n```\n\n### 2. 配置数据库\n\n编辑 `appsettings.json` 或 `appsettings.Development.json`，修改数据库连接字符串：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"ConnectionStrings\": {\n    \"PostgreSQL\": \"Host=localhost;Port=5432;Database=tianyou;Username=postgres;Password=yourpassword\"\n  }\n}\n```\n\n### 3. 运行数据库迁移\n\n```bash\ndotnet ef migrations add InitialCreate\ndotnet ef database update\n```\n\n### 4. 运行服务\n\n```bash\ndotnet run\n```\n\n服务将在 `http://localhost:5000` 启动。\n\n### 5. 查看 API 文档\n\n访问 Swagger UI: `http://localhost:5000/swagger`\n\n## API 端点\n\n### 表单 API (`/api/form`)\n\n| 方法 | 端点 | 描述 |\n|------|------|------|\n| GET | `/metadata/{formCode}` | 获取表单元数据 |\n| GET | `/data/{dataId}` | 获取表单数据 |\n| GET | `/data?formCode=xxx&page=1&pageSize=20` | 获取表单数据列表 |\n| POST | `/data` | 保存表单数据 |\n| DELETE | `/data/{dataId}` | 删除表单数据 |\n| DELETE | `/data` | 批量删除表单数据 |\n| POST | `/validate` | 验证表单数据 |\n| POST | `/evaluate` | 计算表达式 |\n| GET | `/config/{formCode}` | 获取表单配置 |\n\n### 插件 API (`/api/plugin`)\n\n| 方法 | 端点 | 描述 |\n|------|------|------|\n| GET | `/` | 获取所有插件 |\n| GET | `/{pluginId}` | 获取插件详情 |\n| POST | `/load` | 加载插件 |\n| POST | `/{pluginId}/start` | 启动插件 |\n| POST | `/{pluginId}/stop` | 停止插件 |\n| DELETE | `/{pluginId}` | 卸载插件 |\n| POST | `/start-all` | 启动所有插件 |\n| POST | `/stop-all` | 停止所有插件 |\n| POST | `/reload` | 重新加载所有插件 |\n| GET | `/stats` | 获取插件统计 |\n\n## 使用示例\n\n### 获取表单元数据\n\n```bash\ncurl http://localhost:5000/api/form/metadata/sample-form\n```\n\n### 保存表单数据\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/form/data \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"formCode\": \"sample-form\",\n    \"data\": {\n      \"name\": \"张三\",\n      \"age\": 30,\n      \"email\": \"zhangsan@example.com\"\n    },\n    \"userId\": \"user001\",\n    \"userName\": \"张三\"\n  }'\n```\n\n### 计算表达式\n\n```bash\ncurl -X POST http://localhost:5000/api/form/evaluate \\\n  -H \"Content-Type: application/json\" \\\n  -d '{\n    \"expression\": \"{price} * {quantity}\",\n    \"context\": {\n      \"price\": 100,\n      \"quantity\": 5\n    }\n  }'\n```\n\n### 获取所有插件\n\n```bash\ncurl http://localhost:5000/api/plugin/\n```\n\n## 配置说明\n\n### 数据库配置\n\n- **PostgreSQL**: 主数据库，存储表单元数据和业务数据\n- **Redis**: 缓存服务，提升性能\n\n### 插件目录\n\n默认插件目录为 `./plugins`，可在配置文件中修改：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"PluginDirectory\": \"./plugins\"\n}\n```\n\n## 日志\n\n日志文件位于 `logs/` 目录，按天滚动：\n\n- `tianyou-YYYYMMDD.txt`: 应用日志\n\n日志级别可在配置文件中调整。\n\n## 健康检查\n\n```bash\ncurl http://localhost:5000/health\n```\n\n返回示例：\n\n```json\n{\n  \"Status\": \"Healthy\",\n  \"Timestamp\": \"2026-03-22T14:00:00Z\",\n  \"Service\": \"Tianyou Form Service\"\n}\n```\n\n## 生产部署\n\n### Docker 部署\n\n```dockerfile\nFROM mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/aspnet:8.0 AS base\nWORKDIR /app\n\nFROM mcr.microsoft.com/dotnet/sdk:8.0 AS build\nWORKDIR /src\nCOPY . .\nRUN dotnet restore\nRUN dotnet publish -c Release -o /app/publish\n\nFROM base AS final\nWORKDIR /app\nCOPY --from=build /app/publish .\nEXPOSE 5000\nENTRYPOINT [\"dotnet\", \"Tianyou.FormService.dll\"]\n```\n\n### 环境变量\n\n- `ConnectionStrings__PostgreSQL`: PostgreSQL 连接字符串\n- `Redis__ConnectionString`: Redis 连接字符串\n- `PluginDirectory`: 插件目录路径\n\n## 常见问题\n\n### 1. 数据库连接失败\n\n检查 PostgreSQL 服务是否运行，连接字符串是否正确。\n\n### 2. 插件加载失败\n\n检查插件 DLL 文件是否存在，依赖项是否完整。\n\n### 3. Redis 连接失败\n\n检查 Redis 服务是否运行，缓存服务会自动降级为内存缓存。\n\n## 许可证\n\nMIT License\n","path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/services/Tianyou.FormService/README.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":41,"output":1415,"cacheRead":47792,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":49248,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774188146376}}
