\n- **PostgreSQL**: 主数据库\n- **Dapper**: SQL 查询\n- **Redis**: 缓存服务\n- **ASP.NET Core**: Web API 框架\n- **Serilog**: 日志记录\n- **Swagger**: API 文档\n\n## 命名空间\n\n所有代码使用 `Tianyou.*` 命名空间，不包含任何第三方品牌名称。\n","path":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-silijian/projects/tianyou-dotnet/PROJECT_STRUCTURE.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"zai","model":"glm-4.7","usage":{"input":1369,"output":1290,"cacheRead":53121,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":55780,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774188213268}}
